          "language": "py",
          "contents": "import random\n\n# Roll the dice 5 times\ncount = 0\nwhile count < 5: # Modify this number so the dice is rolled 10 times. \n    dice_roll = random.randint(1, 6) # This code will generate a random number between 1 and 6 each time it is executed. \n    print(\"You rolled a\", dice_roll)\n    count += 1",
